lm-left-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/fc3ebfcb-4da2-4786-99f9-5d46fecb8236/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Heimundgarten-Journal_4ba1ea53-fe02-4296-a975-1c2b7218b260.avif" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="20%" data-height="auto" title="" width="300" height="90" natural-width="300" natural-height="90" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709026996382" class="gf_row gf_row-fluid gf_row-no-padding gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709026996382" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" data-row-gap="0px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1685509315590" data-id="1685509315590"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996356" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709026996356"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Das perfekte Geschenk für Tierliebhaber: eine einzigartige, handgefertigte Lampe, die Ihr Herz und Ihr Zuhause erhellt.</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996419" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996419"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#878282">Konrad Cronenberg | Advertorial | Publiziert vor 2 Stunden</font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1752264862134" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1752264862134" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/30ac4cbc-1f84-448f-ae9b-572f93d87f01-ezgif.com-gif-to-webp-converter_120x120.webp?v=1754993978" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="800" natural-height="450" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996388" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996388"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Wenn ich an die schönsten Erinnerungen meines Lebens denke, sind viele davon mit meiner lebenslangen Faszination für den Elefanten verbunden. Für mich ist er ein Symbol für Stärke, Treue und diese unbeschreibliche Ruhe, die er ausstrahlt.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Schon als Kind habe ich mich für Elefanten begeistert. Ich habe Bücher über sie gelesen, Dokus geschaut und Bilder gesammelt. Immer wenn ich einem Elefanten in freier Natur begegnet bin – oder auch nur in einem Wildpark – hat mich sein wachsamer Blick und seine stolze Haltung tief beeindruckt.</span></font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1714045396277" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1714045396277" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/77cb581b-1480-4957-8d5f-31ce61b9e491/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/4.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1713946259430" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1713946259430"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Vor drei Monaten sah ich in einer Zeitschrift ein atemberaubendes Foto eines Elefanten. Es erinnerte mich an all die Momente, in denen ich mich diesem Tier so verbunden gefühlt habe. Seitdem hängt das Bild bei mir im Wohnzimmer, und ich schaue es oft an, um diese besondere Stimmung einzufangen.</span></font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1719233200833" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1719233200833" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Und dann kam ein Geschenk, das alles veränderte …</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1752062029176" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1752062029176"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Es war ein ruhiger Nachmittag. Ich saß mit einer Tasse Tee am Fenster, als es an der Tür klingelte. Ein kleines Paket – von meiner Tochter. Ich erkannte sofort ihre Handschrift.</span></font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1751954804790" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1751954804790" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/c0289d6e-c30d-4d4a-915a-f32c76e68014/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/1.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996416" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996416" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Als ich es öffnete, stockte mir der Atem:</p><p><br></p><p>Eine handgefertigte Elefantenlampe, liebevoll gestaltet, voller Ausdruckskraft. Die wachen Augen, die detailreiche Hautstruktur, die stolze Haltung – all das erinnerte mich an die Magie, die Elefanten für mich schon immer hatten.</p><p><br></p><p>Ich konnte nicht wegsehen. Es war, als würde er gleich aus dem Licht heraustreten.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><